						<summary>

						<p>Registers the gift of a bronze lamp and 9000 <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> towards supply of ghee for the same at the rate of 1 <hi rend="italic">nāḻi</hi> per day to Aḻagiyamaṇavāḷapperumāḷ by Mādhavaṉ Ayirkkāḍaṉ of Muruṇōttamaṅgalam in Malaimaṇḍalam. The record is dated in the <hi rend="bold">18th regnal year</hi> of the king.</p>						

						<p>Published in the <hi rend="italic">S.I.I.,</hi> Vol. IV, No. 510.</p>						

						</summary>
